[preparation]
- warm bowl then dry with tea towel

[base matcha]
- sift 2g (per serve) through sieve into bowl
- add 60g water at 75Â°C 
- whisk in a linear motion, not circular, and without touching the bottom, to stir up foam

[latte]
- steam 200g milk with 5g sugar as abrasive
- optionally add:
  - 10g honey
  - 20g strawberry jam

[iced strwaberry]
- matcha as above
- 150g milk
- 10g honey
- 40g strawberry mix (boiled down bag of frozen strawberries)

[simple strawbery]
- matcha as above
- 200g milk
- 12g strawberry nesquik
- 30g strawberry jam/mix
- optionally cubed ice
